Package: awrms
Version: 1.0
Section: web
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Maintainer: AWRMS Packager <noreply@example.com>
Depends: nginx, php, php-mysql, mariadb-server, icecast2, wget
Description: Automated Web Radio Management Suite (AWRMS)
 A minimal installer package that places the AWRMS web app under /var/www/html/awrms,
 provides an nginx vhost and sample SQL schema. Post-install scripts attempt to create
 the database and enable the nginx site. This package implements a minimal PHP app per PRD.
